    "D. Symmetry AnalysisBefore presenting the numerical results it is useful to summarize how a perpendicular static field modifies the point-group symmetry of the systems considered.",
    "The symmetry fixes which components of the second-order conductivity tensor σ(2) abc [57] can be nonzero and explains the different qualitative responses of monolayer, 2H bilayer, and 3R bilayer MoS 2.",
